{"ja395:0.1":"Jataka ","ja395:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","ja395:0.3":"Kharaputtavagga ","ja395:0.4":"10. Paravatajataka ","ja395:1.1":"“Cirassam vata passami, ","ja395:1.2":"sahayam manidharinam; ","ja395:1.3":"Sukata massukuttiya, ","ja395:1.4":"sobhate vata me sakha”. ","ja395:2.1":"“Parulhakacchanakhalomo, ","ja395:2.2":"aham kammesu byavato; ","ja395:2.3":"Cirassam nhapitam laddha, ","ja395:2.4":"lomam tam ajja harayim”. ","ja395:3.1":"“Yannu lomam aharesi, ","ja395:3.2":"dullabham laddha kappakam; ","ja395:3.3":"Atha kincarahi te samma, ","ja395:3.4":"kanthe kinikinayati”. ","ja395:4.1":"“Manussasukhumalanam, ","ja395:4.2":"mani kanthesu lambati; ","ja395:4.3":"Tesaham anusikkhami, ","ja395:4.4":"ma tvam manni dava katam. ","ja395:5.1":"Sacepimam pihayasi, ","ja395:5.2":"massukuttim sukaritam; ","ja395:5.3":"Karayissami te samma, ","ja395:5.4":"manincapi dadami te”. ","ja395:6.1":"“Tvanneva manina channo, ","ja395:6.2":"Sukataya ca massuya; ","ja395:6.3":"Amanta kho tam gacchami, ","ja395:6.4":"Piyam me tavadassanan”ti. ","ja395:7.1":"Paravatajatakam dasamam. ","ja395:7.2":"Kharaputtavaggo dutiyo. ","ja395:8.1":"Tassuddanam ","ja395:9.1":"Atha passa sasuci ca tundilako, ","ja395:9.2":"Miga mayhakapancamapakkhivaro; ","ja395:9.3":"Atha panjali varija mejjha puna, ","ja395:9.4":"Atha vatta kapotavarena dasati. ","ja395:10.1":"Atha vagguddanam ","ja395:11.1":"Atha vaggam pakittissam, ","ja395:11.2":"chanipatam varuttame; ","ja395:11.3":"Avariya ca kharo ca, ","ja395:11.4":"dve ca vutta subyanjanati. ","ja395:12.1":"Chakkanipatam nitthitam. "}